title: How to Do Warrior Braids | AXE | Instagroom
description:
This is how Flavio keeps it rock and roll: with thick eyebrows and warrior braids.

THE TOOLS:
AXE Natural Look Softening Cream 
Hairband

THE STEPS:
1. Brush and cream to smooth
2. Divide hair in three even sections
3. Cross the right section over the middle section
4. Cross left section over the middle section
5. Cross again and repeat
6. Lock it with a hairband

Subscribe to the AXE channel for more grooming tips.

transcripts: I think my eyebrows are probably the most noticeable thing about me. Alright braids, brush it out first, apply some hair cream. Part my hair and braiding into three even strands, cross­over, cross­over, cross­over until you reach the tip of your hair. Whack on that elastic band.
